OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,7,FSarah Corker and Senior Producer
OL,8,FLottie Kilraine report
OL,10,FThe health secretary has admitted "the
OL,11,Fstate got this wrong" after a year-
OL,12,Flong ITV News investigation exposed
OL,13,Fthe scale of the harm caused by the
OL,14,FDES pregnancy drug scandal, which was
OL,15,Fprescribed to women on the NHS for
OL,16,Fdecades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
