OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,7,Fadmitted the 'state got this wrong'
OL,8,Fafter a year-long ITV News
OL,9,Finvestigation exposed the scale of the
OL,10,Fharm caused by the DES pregnancy drug
OL,11,Fscandal
OL,13,F"I think ITV have done a brilliant job
OL,14,Fin bringing the lived reality to life
OL,15,Fof what's happened with these cases,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
