OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,F"There's a sense of responsibility the
OL,7,Fstate has to show. The first is
OL,8,Fhonesty, that the state got this
OL,9,Fwrong, and that is why I am
OL,10,Fapologising on behalf of the state,
OL,11,Fand on behalf of the government today,
OL,12,Ffor historic injustice.
OL,14,F"The important thing now also is that
OL,15,Fwe get people the right support. So,
OL,16,Fif there are people watching this who
OL,17,Fthink they may have been affected by
OL,18,Fthis, I urge them to go and see their
OL,19,FGP to raise their concerns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
