OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,F"There is screening available, there
OL,7,Fis support available, and I will
OL,8,Fcontinue to listen to their members of
OL,9,Fparliament, listen to their calls for
OL,10,Fchange and do everything I can to
OL,11,Fcorrect this historic injustice," he
OL,12,Fadded.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, Streeting wrote a letter
OL,15,Fto victims of the scandal recognising
OL,16,Fand apologising for their "harrowing"
OL,17,Fexperiences, adding that women
OL,18,F"understandably feel that their
OL,19,Fhealthcare system failed".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
