OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,FThis is the first time health
OL,7,Fauthorities have publicly recognised
OL,8,Fthe harm caused by DES, after our
OL,9,Finvestigation exposed that warnings
OL,10,Fabout the sinister side effects of the
OL,11,Fdrug were not acted on for decades.
OL,13,FIn the letter seen by ITV News,
OL,14,FStreeting wrote: "It is only
OL,15,Funderstandable that they feel their
OL,16,Fhealthcare system failed to address
OL,17,Fthis pattern of multigenerational harm
OL,18,Fby inadequately informing people and
OL,19,Fprotecting them from known harmful
OL,20,Feffects of DES."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
