OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,FVictims and campaigners have welcomed
OL,7,Fthe health secretary's apology but say
OL,8,Fhis response "falls short and fails to
OL,9,Faddress accountability".
OL,11,FThe women who believe they were
OL,12,Fexposed to DES tell ITV News about
OL,13,Fhealth problems they fear may be
OL,14,Flinked to the drug. This is their
OL,15,Fstory in their own words.
OL,17,FMore than 400 campaigners formed DES
OL,18,FJustice UK, which launched earlier
OL,19,Fthis month, following ITV News'
OL,20,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
