OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,FClare Fletcher, partner at Broudie
OL,7,FJackson Canter, representing DES
OL,8,FJustice UK, said the group has "mixed
OL,9,Ffeelings about Wes Streeting's
OL,10,Fresponse".
OL,12,F"While it is remarkable to finally be
OL,13,Facknowledged after such a long period
OL,14,Fof being ignored, any promises from
OL,15,Fthe government must be practical and
OL,16,Feffective," she told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
