OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,F"There remains a significant
OL,7,Finformation gap within the GP and
OL,8,Fbroader NHS sectors. Are they to
OL,9,Fattend appointments brandishing a
OL,10,Fletter from the Health Secretary? We
OL,11,Fdo not accept that screening is
OL,12,Fcurrently available, an issue of
OL,13,Furgent concern."
OL,15,FThe group is now calling on the health
OL,16,Fsecretary to meet with them in person
OL,17,Fto hear their stories first-hand and
OL,18,Flaunch a full statutory public
OL,19,Finquiry, with clear recommendations
OL,20,Ffollowed by swift actions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
