OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Health secretary
OL,4,Cadmits 'state got this wrong'
OL,6,F"We seek justice, transparency, and
OL,7,Freal action - not just words," Ms
OL,8,FFletcher added. "We call for a
OL,9,Fstatutory public inquiry to thoroughly
OL,10,Finvestigate what the government knew,
OL,11,Fwhen they knew it, and why they failed
OL,12,Fto act."
OL,14,FDES, originally called
OL,15,FDiethylstilboestrol, is a synthetic
OL,16,Foestrogen invented in Britain in 1939.
OL,17,FResearch suggests pregnant women who
OL,18,Ftook DES may have a 30% higher risk of
OL,19,Fbreast cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
