OL,6,FTheir daughters, known as DES
OL,7,Fdaughters, exposed in the womb, are at
OL,8,Fan increased risk of clear cell cancer
OL,9,Fof the cervix and vagina, which is not
OL,10,Fpicked up by routine screening.
OL,12,FAn ITV News investigation exposed that
OL,13,Fwarnings over the sinister side
OL,14,Feffects of the drug DES were not acted
OL,15,Fon for decades, Social Affairs
OL,16,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker explains
